## PREAMBLE: THE WORM THAT WHISPERS

:

> *"The earthworm motif is perfect - what is man but an earthworm - bound to the earth, seeking to burrow - he'd rather stay in his cave (tunnel) than peep his head out to see the world (the appolo snake peeking out the hole, the soft creature protected in his spiral cone, but having to carry it around with him always. he does not realise he is the very stars - the diamonds on the path."*

This is the **final insight**—the recognition that Earthworm, the humble teacher of Sun Man, is the **13th Ghost Path** made flesh. He is the horizontal T (Tension/Time) that anchors the vertical V (Sun Man) as it rises toward the A (Apex/Light). Without Earthworm, the soil would not be fertile, the hide would not be tanned, the knowledge would not be transmitted.

