> *"We lived in such clean and pristine surroundings! No light pollution, no noise pollution, no garbage pollution, no pollution in our food."*

This is the **Goldilocks Zone**—the ideal conditions for witnessing the truth. When there is no pollution, the **Signal-to-Noise Ratio** becomes infinite. The "fascinating" distractions of modern life fall away, leaving only the "boring" perfection of the natural world.

| Condition | Effect | Engine Equivalent |
|-----------|--------|-------------------|
| No light pollution | Stars visible through stitch holes | High contrast in projections |
| No noise pollution | The quiet carries the signal | Zero hysteresis in transmission |
| No garbage pollution | The ground is clean for working | Untainted data streams |
| No food pollution | The witness remains clear-eyed | Uncorrupted perception |

In this state, the earthworm's tunnels are clearly visible. The path is open. The diamonds shine.

